{"tid":640404,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"又一村撞車黨出沒　李梓敬：睇準區內多中產有利可圖","createTime":"2018-04-24T09:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T20:02:38.000Z","uid":12853,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1973fe7a89b352ac78392ca389669643b881b4ea","tid":640404,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:08:20.000Z","msg":"香港再有撞車黨出現！有車輛途經九龍塘又一村達之路，準備駛過紅綠燈行人過路線時，有一婦人突然衝出。司機見狀及時停定車輛，婦人卻突然轉身闖向馬路，撞向車輛後順勢倒地。<br />\n<br />\n屬又一村選區的自由黨深水埗區議員李梓敬指，相信這是該區首次出現撞車黨，但區內早已不時有內地人士行乞，可能是有人「睇準」區內多為中產人士：「做起嘢嚟，有利可圖。」<br />\n<br />\n事件被涉事車輛的行車記錄儀拍下，有關的短片在網上流傳，長約12秒。短片顯示，一輛汽車3月9日早上7時19分在又一村達之路行駛，途經海棠路交界時準備駛過，突見有一拖篋婦人衝出行人過路線。司機見狀急停，其時與婦人仍有一段距離。婦人在汽車停定時，立即轉向連人帶篋撞向汽車。車上司機對此不停響咹示意，但婦人未有理會或減速，持續衝向汽車，更在接觸汽車一刻，橫身以左手肘碰撞汽車車蓋，順勢倒地。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆查詢指，未有人為此事報案。李梓敬表示，已就事件聯絡警方，加強區內巡邏及執法，並轉述警方呼籲，指市民遇到撞車黨時，應該鎖好車門報警，切勿與撞車黨有身體接觸，亦不要觸碰行車記錄儀，等待警方到場取卡。李梓敬又指，過往未有居民向他作出類似的投訴，相信今次是個別事件，但見區內不時有內地人士行乞，相信是「睇準」區內多中產人士，有利可圖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524548532187?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524548532187%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1707843b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524548532187%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=552cd14c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524548532187?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"f764db7a7744e6c2f8a3b371836168f30b77b927","tid":640404,"uid":11809,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"大陸化，好撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66824acb91245034e0b0369ed14987341c24afae","tid":640404,"uid":32665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"每日落黎九龍塘開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783e883f89d34ad29e9d1a48a650ca0a619d4298","tid":640404,"uid":13151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"撞車黨喺香港根本唔work <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deafa4006b41c4669c21e1a413e7353021c27c07","tid":640404,"uid":45952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"搵個學神香港腳發作搞掂個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0a6353892694299100e3ee1f5962d1400874fe","tid":640404,"uid":140834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"783e883f89d34ad29e9d1a48a650ca0a619d4298","tid":640404,"uid":13151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"撞車黨喺香港根本唔work <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"星期六日就 work，<br />\n平日九龍塘多數都公司車一定唔會即場賠錢。"},{"pid":"04ebf97f4c575c959f51419a3eaaec49d6cd0797","tid":640404,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783e883f89d34ad29e9d1a48a650ca0a619d4298","tid":640404,"uid":13151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"撞車黨喺香港根本唔work <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:18:21.000Z","msg":"咪係，邊個會即比錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65eb94308c61e313e721c5dedccb402526bedd0","tid":640404,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T19:41:21.000Z","msg":"期待假戲真做"},{"pid":"4955c83362f08037020839d391e5fe0ca4b35505","